    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The governing requirement specifies 'adequate predictive fidelity' and 'clinically acceptable hemolysis performance'; the assessment team determined that the observed RH values (0.71–0.94, all below the RH < 1 threshold) and output comparison results constitute reasonable agreement consistent with accepted practice for Class II devices. The specific numerical threshold for 'reasonable agreement' is defined in internal document MP-CFD-HEM-007 and is considered satisfied by the responsible engineering team. Decision: Accepted for regulatory submission.",
